Movie Info: Lucia is an Indian Kannada language psychological thriller film directed and written by Pawan Kumar. It stars Satish Neenasam and Sruthi Hariharan.

The trailer of Lucia was released in February 2013,with the film releasing on September 6,2013. Lucia premiered at the London Indian Film Festival on July 20, 2013 along with some Hindi movies like Monsoon Shootout and Bombay Talkies directed by Anurag Kashyap. It won the Best Film Audience Choice award at the festival.

